1
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,000
Vivi,

2
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,040
I'll take you to the hospital.

3
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:15,600
It must hurt a lot.

4
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,400
I'm sorry.

5
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:25,160
I shouldn't have made the decision myself.

6
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,480
I shouldn't have hidden it from you.

7
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,400
As long as you get better,

8
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:39,000
we can be like we used to be.

9
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:44,960
Mengmeng,

10
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,720
I don't have much time left.

11
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,960
I want to go home.

12
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:57,960
Okay.

13
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:00,920
I'll take you home.

14
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,440
I'll take you home.

15
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,200
Mengmeng,

16
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:16,400
don't be sad.

17
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,520
You are alive,

18
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,800
so I am alive.

19
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:32,560
Vivi,

20
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:38,000
bring me the comb.

21
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,760
I'm washing my face.

22
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,200
It's on my pillow.

23
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,320
Get it yourself.

24
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,640
Mengmeng,

25
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:51,080
Do you think I can win a prize in the music competition

26
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,080
in a few days?

27
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,520
You're so good.
You can do it.

28
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,160
What about you?

29
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,600
What's your dream?

30
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,280
Since I can remember,

31
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,120
I've been living in an orphanage.

32
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,800
My parents gave me a home.

33
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,160
So when I grow up,

34
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,160
I want all the orphans

35
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,120
to have a home.

36
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,360
You will make it.

37
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:18,800
Let's work hard together.

38
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,400
Why did you come back so late today?

39
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,000
Don't mention it.

40
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,840
Today there was a senior

41
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,280
named Lin Mojiao.

42
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:33,360
He insisted on adding me on WeChat.

43
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,080
I didn't want to add him at all.

44
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,440
Don't talk about it.
I'm sleepy.

45
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,520
Go to sleep.

46
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:44,800
Go to sleep.
Go to sleep.

47
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,320
When did you go to see Vivi?

48
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,200
Don't make a sound.

49
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,360
I'll take you away from here.

50
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:06,880
Mr. Zhen,

51
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,880
I heard you calling Mengmeng

52
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,200
in the sanatorium before.

53
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,640
Let's get out of here first.

54
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:19,840
I can't go with you.

55
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,320
I don't have much time left.

56
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,200
I'm worried that Lin Mojiao

57
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,240
will take action against Mengmeng.

58
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,240
[That's why I chose]

59
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,840
[to use such a cruel method.]

60
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,800
[This time,]

61
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,480
[I'll protect her.]

62
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,360
[Please give this share transfer agreement]

63
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:56,640
[to Mengmeng.]

64
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,480
[I'll also record a video]

65
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:11,000
[to expose Lin Mojiao's crimes.]

66
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:14,600
[I hope it will help you.]

67
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,280
I...

68
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:38,200
Lan Hewei

69
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,840
hereby announces

70
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,960
after my death,

71
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:44,040
all my properties,

72
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,640
the presidency of Lanhe Group,

73
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:49,400
and all shares in Lanhe

74
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,640
will be transferred to Xu Meng.

75
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,120
My husband Lin Mojiao

76
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,520
coveted my properties.

77
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:58,200
On our wedding day,

78
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:00,440
he forged a bribery case to frame my parents,

79
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,360
and attacked me in the abandoned tower,

80
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:06,120
pushing me off the building.

81
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,960
That caused my coma for over a year.

82
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,160
After I woke up,

83
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,280
he tricked me into

84
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:16,080
signing the resort project agreement,

85
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,840
trying to take over Blue Crane.

86
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,280
With this video as proof,

87
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,560
that document is null and void.

88
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,280
My property

89
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:23,720
goes to Xu Meng alone.

90
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:26,080
I was not threatened by anyone.

91
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:29,480
This video was voluntarily recorded at Lin Mojiao's home.

92
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:30,680
Later,

93
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,360
my lawyer will notarize it.

94
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,360
The water is just right.

95
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,320
Have some.

96
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:24,640
Don't drink alcohol

97
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:26,200
during pregnancy.

98
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:43,040
Go cook after you're done.

99
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,040
I'm hungry.

100
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,120
What's wrong?

101
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:22,200
Are you hurt?

102
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:27,680
Does it hurt?

103
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:25,360
Sister.

104
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,680
Have this.

105
00:14:52,400 --> 00:14:53,200
Mr. Zhu.

106
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:55,360
This cooperation will be a very good start

107
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:57,160
for us.

108
00:14:57,800 --> 00:14:58,600
I also hope

109
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,880
you can keep your word.

110
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:02,920
The Lin family has been through a lot lately.

111
00:15:03,160 --> 00:15:04,680
Don't make any more mistakes.

112
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:06,680
Since we're on this topic,

113
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,400
I have one more thing to say.

114
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:10,680
Okay.

115
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:15,000
I want to marry Wenjie.

116
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:20,640
Mr. Lin,

117
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:23,360
your wife just died.

118
00:15:24,800 --> 00:15:26,680
isn't it a bit too hasty?

119
00:15:43,520 --> 00:15:44,000
Mr. Zhu,

120
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:48,120
don't think your daughter has any commercial value.

121
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:50,200
Zhu Wenjie is pregnant out of wedlock.

122
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,920
If this gets out,

123
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:55,400
it will not only ruin her reputation,

124
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,560
but also the interests of Zhu Rong.

125
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,520
Are you threatening me?

126
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:05,320
Uncle,

127
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:08,400
don't put it so harshly.

128
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:11,120
As long as you agree,

129
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:12,600
next,

130
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:16,000
our business status in Hai City

131
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:18,120
will be unmatched.
